#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today we are learning about giving our children praise. \n"
"\n"
"Praise helps build a positive relationship and encourages good behaviour!\n"
"\n"
"Let’s first reflect on our own experience with praise."
msgstr ""
"Namhlanje sifunda ngokunika abantwana bethu izincomo.\n"
"\n"
"Ukuncoma kunceda ukwakha ubundlelwane obuhle kwaye kukhuthaza nokuziphatha kakuhle.\n"
"\n"
"Masiqale sicacise ngamava ethu ngokuncoma."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Think about the last time someone thanked you, or said you did something great."
msgstr "Cinga ngokugqibela kwakho ukubulelwa ngumntu okanye wakuxelela ukuba wenze into esemagqabini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How did it make you feel?"
msgstr "Yakwenza waziva njani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Proud"
msgstr "Benebhongo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Being praised often makes us feel proud."
msgstr "Kuhle kakhulu! Ukunconywa ngamaxesha amaninzi kusenza sizive sinebhongo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Happy"
msgstr "Uyavuya"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Being praised often makes us feel happy!"
msgstr "Kuhle kakhulu! Ukunconywa ngamaxesha amaninzi kusenza sizive sonwabile!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Embarrassed"
msgstr "Ndineentloni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes being praised makes us feel embarrassed, usually because we are not used to it. Remember, everybody deserves praise!"
msgstr "Ngamanye amaxesha ukunconywa kusenza sizive sineentloni, ngokuqhelekileyo ngenxa yokuba asiqhelanga. Khumbula, wonke umntu ufanelwe kukunconywa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"We all feel better when we are praised.\n"
"\n"
"Praising your child when they behave well will make them want to behave that way more often. \n"
"\n"
"It also creates a positive and loving relationship between you."
msgstr ""
"Sonke siziva ngcono xa sinconywa.\n"
"\n"
"Ukuncoma umntwana wakho xa eziphethebkakuhle kuya kumenza afune ukuziphatha ngolo hlobo rhoqo.\n"
"\n"
"Kukwadala ubudlelwane obuhle nobunothando phakathi kwakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tap play to hear how praise can help you and your family"
msgstr "Cofa udlala umamele ukuba ukuncoma kungakunceda njani ena nosapho lwakho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"When was the last time you were praised? Can you praise yourself for something right now? Praise makes us all feel good. \n"
"\n"
"It is good to praise our children when they have done well, because when we do that, they will do more of that good behaviour we want to see.\n"
"\n"
"And let's remember to praise ourselves too, for big or small things!"
msgstr ""
"Molweni nonke.\n"
"\n"
"Ugqibele nini ukunconywa? uyakwazi ukuzincoma ngento ngoku? Ukuncoma kusenza sizive sonwabile.\n"
"\n"
"Kuhle ukubancoma abantwana bethu xa benze kakuhle. kuba xa sisenza loo nto, kwenza ngakumbi ngendlela esifuna ukuyibona.\n"
"\n"
"Kwaye masikhumbule ukuzincoma nathi ngezinto ezinkulu okanye ezincinci.\n"
"\n"
"!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s look at how @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises her son, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, during one-on-one time."
msgstr "Masibone benze njani u@data.characters.f3_mother.name kunye nonyana wakhe u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name kusuku olulandelayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You found one striped sock and one with dots. Let’s find socks that match."
msgstr "Ufumene iikawusi ezinemigca enye kwaye enye inamachokoza. Masifumane iikawusi ezihambelanayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Another sock! This one is white. It’s frustrating to try to find a matching pair when there are so many clothes to look through."
msgstr "Enye ikawusi! lena imhlophe. Iyakhathaza ukuzama ukufumana iperiehambelanayo zininzi iimpahla onokuzijonga."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You are being very patient and looking very hard, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name. Well done for trying. I am happy you are helping me."
msgstr "Unomonde kwaye ujongeka unzima kakhulu,@data.characters.f3_son_4.name wenze kakuhle ngokuzama.Ndiyavuya undincedisa mna."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"You found two socks with the same pattern! Well done for not giving up, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name! \n"
"\n"
"Because you helped me so well, I now have 5 extra minutes to play with you. What would you like to do?"
msgstr ""
"Ufumene iikawusi ezimbini ezinepateni efanayo! Wenze kakuhle ngokunganikezeli @data.characters.f3_son_4.name@data.characters.f3_son_4.name!\n"
"\n"
"Kuba undinceda kakuhle, ngoku ndinemizuzu 5 eyongezelelweyo yokudlala nawe.Ingaba ungathanda ukwenza into?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s reflect on how @data.characters.f3_mother.name praised her son."
msgstr "Khawucinge ngendlela @data.characters.f3_mother.name amncoma ngayo unyana wakhe."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When @data.characters.f3_mother.name gives @data.characters.f3_son_4.name a hug and extra playtime together, she rewards him and encourages him to stay patient and keep helping with chores."
msgstr "Xa u@data.characters.f3_mother.name esanga u@data.characters.f3_son_4.namekwaye enexeshaelongezelelekileyo lokudlala kunye, uyamvuza aze amkhuthaze ukuba athethe ngomonde aze aqhubeke encedisa kwimisebenzi yasekhaya."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why does @data.characters.f3_mother.name praise her son?"
msgstr "Kutheni u@data.characters.f3_mother.name encoma unyana wakhe?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To boost confidence"
msgstr "Ukwandisa ukuzithemba"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, he feels good about himself.\n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Xa u@data.characters.f3_mother.name encoma u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name uziva kamnandi ngaye.\n"
"lonke olukhetho liyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To help him deal with his frustration"
msgstr "Ukumnceda ahlangabezane nengxaki zakhe"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Exactly! When @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, he will want to keep looking for the socks.\n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Kanye!xau@data.characters.f3_mother.name encoma@data.characters.f3_son_4.name uya kufuna ukuqhubeka ekhangela iikawusi.\n"
"Lonke olukhetho luyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To encourage him to want to help more often"
msgstr "Ukukhuthaza ukuba afune ukunceda rhoqo"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Exactly! When @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, he will feel good and be more likely to help with chores in the future.\n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Kanye! xa u@data.characters.f3_mother.name encoma u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name,uya kuziva onwabile kwaye kunokwenzeka ukuba ancedise kwimisebenzi yasekhaya kwixesha elizayo.\n"
"Lonke olukhetho luyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s see what we can learn from HOW @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises her son."
msgstr "Makhe sibone ukuba yintoni esinokuyifunda kwindlela@data.characters.f3_mother.name ancoma ngayo unyana wakhe."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name’s
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name’s
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f3_mother.name’s praise works because she: \n"
"- 🫱🏾‍🫲🏽 Goes down to @data.characters.f3_son_4.name’s level\n"
"- 👀 Uses his name and makes eye contact\n"
"- 👏🏾 Praises his behaviour right after it happens\n"
"- 👍🏾 Praises him for trying, not for the successful outcome\n"
"- 💜 Does not criticise his mistake"
msgstr ""
"@data.characters.f3_mother.name uncoma umsebenzi ngokuba yena\n"
"-🫱🏾‍🫲🏽 Wehlile @data.characters.f3_son_4.name wakwinqanaba elisezantsi\n"
"-👀Usebenzise igama lakhe kwaye wamjonga emehlweni\n"
"-👏🏾Uyayincoma indlela aziphatha ngayo emva kokuba yenzekile\n"
"-👍🏾Uyamncoma ngokuzama, kungekho neziphumo eziyimpumelelo\n"
"-💜 Akazingxeki impazamo zakhe"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Simple and free rewards can help reinforce praise. What rewards does @data.characters.f3_mother.name use?"
msgstr "Imivuzo elula kunye nesimahla inokunceda ukuqinisa izincomo.Yeyiphi imivuzo esetyenziswa@data.characters.f3_mother.name?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A hug"
msgstr "Ngamanga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Extra playtime together"
msgstr "Ixesha lokudlala elongezelelweyo kunye"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right, giving a simple and free reward helps our children to do behaviours that may be difficult for them."
msgstr "Kulungile! ukunika imbuyekezo elula nesimahla kunceda abantwana bethu benze izinto ezinokuba nzima kubo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some easy tips for how to use praise."
msgstr "Nazi ezinye indlela ezilula zokusebenzisa ukuncoma."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEE IT"
msgstr "YIBONE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look for good behaviours that you can praise! It can be anything positive or helpful your child does or tries to do."
msgstr "Khangela indlela entle yokuziphatha unokuyincoma! Inokuba yiyo nayiphina into eluncedo eyenziwa ngumntwana okanye azama ukuyenza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Pause and really notice when they are doing something positive. Even if it’s expected of them.\n"
"\n"
"Praise your child for *trying*. This boosts their self-esteem and confidence, which helps them to learn new behaviours."
msgstr ""
"Yima kwaye uqaphele ngokwenene xa benza into eyakhayo. Nokuba kulindeleke kubo.\n"
"\n"
"Mncome umntwana wakho *ngokuzama*. Oku kukhulisa ukuzazi nokuzithemba okubanceda bafunde inlela entsha yokuziphatha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SAY IT"
msgstr "YITHETHE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise them when you see them do something you like. Do this every day – even if it’s something really small."
msgstr "Bancome xa ubabona besenza into oyithandayo. Yenza oku yonke mihla nokuba yinto encinci kakhulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Tell them specifically what they have done well.\n"
"\n"
"Be enthusiastic and really mean it!\n"
"\n"
"You can show your praise with a big smile and words."
msgstr ""
"Baxelele ngokuthe ngqo oko bakwenzileyo kakuhle.\n"
"\n"
"Yiba nomdla kwaye uzimisele ngokwenene!\n"
"\n"
"Ungabonisa ukuncoma kwakho ngoncumo olukhulu kunye nangamagama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "REWARD IT"
msgstr "MVUZE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Give your child a simple, free reward to encourage them to do more of the behaviours that may be difficult for them."
msgstr "Nika umntwana wakho umvuzo olula, wasimahla wokumkhuthaza ukuba enze ngakumbi iindlela zokuziphatha ezinokuba nzima kuye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye ingcebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Give your child a hug, extra playtime together, or make their favourite meal. \n"
"\n"
"Simple rewards can be a big motivation for your child to keep trying and show more positive behaviour."
msgstr ""
"Mange umntwana wakho, ixesha elongezelelweyo likudlala kunye, okanye wenze isidlo asithandayo!\n"
"\n"
"Imivuzo elula ingaba yinkuthazo enkulu kumntwana wakho ukuba aqhubeke ezama kwaye abonise ukuziphatha okulungileyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now that you have learned a few tips on how to use praise, let’s think of specific things we can praise our children for."
msgstr "Ngoku ekubeni ufunde amacebiso ambalwa okusebenzisa ukuncoma, makhe sicinge ngezinto ezithile esinokuncoma ngazo abantwana bethu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What is one behaviour your child regularly shows that you can praise them for?"
msgstr "Yeyiphi enyindlela umntwana wakho aziphatha ngayo ebonisa ukuba unokumncoma ngayo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cleaning up or helping out"
msgstr "Ukucoca okanye ukunceda"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Being patient or polite"
msgstr "Ukuba nomonde oknye imbeko"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Trying a new skill"
msgstr "Ukuzama isakhono esitsha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Playing quietly"
msgstr "Edlala ngokuzolileyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Getting ready for school or bed"
msgstr "Ukulungiselela ukuya esikolweni okanye ukulala"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, you can praise them for these behaviours… and many more!"
msgstr "Ewe, unokubancoma ngezindlela zokuziphatha... kunye nezinye ezininzi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Other"
msgstr "Enye indlela"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Whatever you choose to praise your child for is a great choice. You can praise them whenever they have done something well."
msgstr "Nantoni na okhetha ukuyincoma ngomntwana wakho lukhetho olukhulu olo. Unokumncoma nanini na xa benze into entle."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Your home activity is to praise your child for at least 2 things every day.\n"
"Praise yourself too for all your hard work being a parent – you deserve it!"
msgstr ""
"Umsebenzi wakho wasekhaya kukuncoma umntwana wakho ubuncinane ngezinto ezi2 yonke imihla.\n"
"Zincome nawe ngawo wonke umsebenzi wakhoonzima wokuba ngumzali-ikufanele lonto!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_2.name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tap play to hear how simple praises helped @data.characters.media_female_2.name's family"
msgstr "Cofa udlala ukuze umamele ukuncoma kuncede u@data.characters.media_female_2.name nosapho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When we learned about this praising thing, I thought “We were never praised for things as children, so why should we start now?”. But I got interested when I learned what the benefits of praising could be.\n"
"\n"
"Right after learning about praise, I noticed my son doing what he does every day: Packing away his toys after playing. And I said “Thank you for packing away your toys, my boy, it really makes me happy that you are helping out to keep the house tidy.” My son was smiling and he even came to give me a hug, which he never does. \n"
"\n"
"This praising business is hard. I still forget to do it sometimes. But praising really makes a difference. I never thought that a simple praise could make such a change in a person!"
msgstr ""
"Xa sifunda ngalento yokuncoma, ndicinga ukuba, Asinakuze sincome ngezinto njengabantwana ngoko kutheni sifanele siqalise ngoku? Kodwa ndaba nomdla xa ndafunda ngeenzuzo zoncomo ezikhoyo.\n"
"\n"
"Kanye emva kokuba ndifunde ngokuncoma, ndabona unyana wam esenza le nto ayenzayo mihla le. Ukupakisha izinto zakhe zokudlala emva kokudldla, Ndaye ndathi \"Enkosi ngokupakisha izinto zakho zokudlala mfo wam, iyandonwabisa into yokuba uncedise ukugcina indlu icocekile. Unyana wam ebencumile wade wafika wandanga into angazange ayenze.\n"
"\n"
"Ishishini lokuncoma linzima Ndiyalibala ukulenza ngamanye amaxesha. Kodwa ukuncoma kuyawenza umahluko nyani. Zange ndiyicinge into yokuncoma nje inokwenza utshintsho emntwini!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you praise your child today?"
msgstr "Ngaba ungamncoma umntwana wakho namhlanje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Parents who practise praise at home get better results!"
msgstr "Kuhle kakhulu! Abazali abaziqhelanisa nokuncoma ekhaya bafumana iziphumo ezingcono!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try praising your child for something simple at first, like putting away their toy. Praise is a powerful parenting skill!"
msgstr "Ungayenza lonto! Zama ukuncoma umntwanawakho ngento elula ekuqaleni, ubeke into yakhe yokudlala. ukuncoma sisakhono esinamandla sokukhulisa abantwana!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. With time, giving praise will become easier. Try to praise yourself for something first, like _\"Well done for using @global.app_name. It shows you care.\"_"
msgstr "Kulungile. Exesheni, ukuncoma kuzakuya kusiba lula. Zama ukuzincoma ngento kuqala, njengo \"Umsebenzi omhle usebenzisa @global.app_name. Ibonakalisa ukuba uyakhathala\""

